        "description": "We study a variant of a polygon partition problem, introduced by Chung, Iwama, Liao, and Ahn [ISAAC'25]. Given orthogonal unit vectors $\\mathbf{u},\\mathbf{v}\\in \\mathbb{R}^2$ and a polygon $P$ with $n$ vertices, we partition $P$ into connected pieces by cuts parallel to $\\mathbf{v}$ such that each r",
